ll be roasted on open flame and then pulverized.Forthe ritual use they will be burned together with frankincense in a bowl. The resulting haze indeed has a horrible scent but it can thereby make the god of agriculture happy. The result is a slight increase yield of herbal resources in the country.§($2,<,-1) §§
